  "observation": "The getBestAgent function picks the agent with the highest recent EQS. Since all agents score EQS=0 after their first run (no improvement), the selector effectively picks arbitrarily. It should consider which agent has the highest absolute fitness, not just improvement rate.",
  "suggestion": "Seed v2 should rank agents by a composite of absolute fitness and EQS trend. An agent that consistently scores fitness=1.0 should be ranked higher than one that scored 0.8 once with a higher EQS spike.",
  "evidence": [],
  "priority": 2
}
